{"type": "article", "id": 53395, "title": "一个超声波清洗机，帮你快速清洁眼镜首饰剃须刀｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-05-20T23:00:41Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 50411, "name": "Outdoor Element"}, {"id": 50412, "name": "Page Anchor Designs"}, {"id": 39676, "name": "Sancal"}, {"id": 247, "name": "Nendo"}, {"id": 18311, "name": "Native Union"}, {"id": 50413, "name": "Smartclean Asia Limited"}, {"id": 50414, "name": "Rafa García"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 33, "praise_count": 297, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180520212635jpy3cW4xPJi9HZN6.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 13.2px; font: 12.0px 'Helvetica Neue'; color: #222222; -webkit-text-stroke: #222222; background-color: #fdfdfd} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 13.2px; font: 12.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #222222; -webkit-text-stroke: #222222; background-color: #fdfdfd} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #337ab7; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #337ab7} span.s5 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s6 {font-kerning: none; background-color: #ffffff} span.s7 {font: 12.0px 'Helvetica Neue'; font-kerning: none} span.s8 {font: 12.0px 'Helvetica Neue'; text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none; color: #222222; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #222222} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Smartclean Vision.5: A Portable Ultrasonic Cleaner by Smartclean Asia Limited</h3><p>一副好的眼镜通常价格不菲，所以眼镜的保养尤为重要，用软布擦、清水冲还是肥皂洗都难以做到清洗彻底。最近，香港公司 Smartclean 在众筹平台 INDIEGOGO 上推出了一款超声波清洗机。</p><p>和市面上大部分同类型产品相比，它的设计要更为美观，轻巧的机身还能让你将其随身携带。它能够在水中利用超声波震动生成大量气泡，这些气泡会不断破裂，由此产生的冲击波可以抖落藏匿在缝隙当中的污垢、灰尘和油脂。</p><p>它使用起来也非常简单，只要灌满清水并把眼镜放进去，然后开机即可，只需两三分钟就能完成眼镜的清洁。除了眼镜之外，Smartclean 还能用来清洁珠宝首饰、手表和剃须刀等等。早鸟价 66 美元，<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/smartclean-vision-5-a-portable-ultrasonic-cleaner-watches-water?utm_source=Yanko%20Deisgn&amp;utm_medium=Article%20%26%20Facebook&amp;utm_campaign=Yanko%20-%20Crowdfunding%20article#/\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180520212738xLPAaYslvIcMQnBh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180520212739BJQdqrwhL39syMXz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180520212738sotL4bnVDE1eJ53d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180520212740fFYRmg7C1XLr9k20.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805202127411MnuzxR4WDCeiayL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Native Union x La Boite Concept PR / 01 Bluetooth Speaker</h3><p>香港科技配件品牌 Native Union 与法国音响制造商 La Boite Concept 合作推出了一款家用音响 PR / 01。它由木制框架、古铜色铝制旋钮和耐磨纺织隔栏组成，支持多种音频输入形式，结构紧凑小巧的同时为用户提供了高功率、高保真度的音效。</p><p>在结构设计上，PR / 01 将传统的音频接口和支持多设备同时充电的 USB 端口隐藏在一个隐形抽屉内。在音频输入方面，PR / 01 支持蓝牙 Apt-x 连接以及两个支持多种连结形式的 AUX 接口。专门为 Native Union Drop 无线充电器设计的凹槽也让所有拥有 Qi 授权的移动设备利用 PR /01 充电成为了可能。售价 699 英镑，<a href=\"https://www.conranshop.co.uk/pr01-speaker.html?utm_source=nativeunion\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180520212913xrROq6shEk2n5BuS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664844\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805202129142hnF6m95WcMjsSa1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180520212913Qo34x8etmFrqLhRc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180520212913vJF6N4EuDKRIsxkQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180520212914xWvY2nDE5FLOtleQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180520212914HepglzaDZmtUG2db.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180520212914OQrIJ285Ai04RstE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>En by Nendo</h3><p>新作频出的日本设计工作室 Nendo，最近推出了一款介于香烟盒电子烟之间的吸烟设备 En，是日语 中“火”的音译。据设计师介绍，这是一款能够减少吸烟给人体带来的伤害的工具。</p><p>烟叶被置放于小胶囊中，只需轻轻按键，便能将胶囊装入或弹出烟尾，不会有传统香烟的烟灰或火星。吸烟时，点燃烟头后等待 5 至 10 秒便可使用，比电子烟迅速。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180520212942EGP9hFzZw0BxMDQk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667513\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180520212942XlWseIKjq0zEmZYF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667513\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180520212942eTlvnQE0dtGqM3U5.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180520212942Fv8TbwXuZS6dMlro.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667513\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180520212942ckXMUTsWNJC5Pp2h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667513\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.nendo.jp/en/works/en/?erelease\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nendo</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Mousse by Rafa García for Sancal</h3><p>西班牙家具品牌 Sancal 推出模块化沙发系列 Mousse，试图模仿慕斯柔软而轻盈的质地。沙发座椅是用泡沫纤维制成。西班牙设计师 Rafa García 戏称设计的过程“就像穿上了围裙，为用户作一份甜蜜的慕斯，愉悦所有的感官。”</p><p>整个系列提供两种类型的座椅模块盒两种不同的扶手，可以组合搭配使用。另有一个带有两个托盘大小的辅助桌，也可以连接到沙发的扶手、靠背或座椅上。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=b0660lybn4x&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180520213012zJra72cNq90d6vVE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180520213012M0gDYi1IRofVtzZA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018052021301241QSyRtgbWZ7msBn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180520213013xCjDInN0OZoYcX7r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.655245\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Page Anchor by Page Anchor Designs</h3><p>最近，众筹网站 Kickstarter 上线了一款新意十足的书签 Page Anchor。它是一个小金属针，可轻松滑入您的书籍，以防止书页不小心合上。它由 316L 不锈钢打造，另外锚定层镀有 14K 金，保证其抛光金表面的耐久性。</p><p>除了作为书签之外，它也可以是一个辅助读书的小工具，在桌前读书时解放双手。早鸟价 329 瑞典克朗，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/pageanchor/page-anchor-making-you-read-more-through-nordic-de?ref=192fiw\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试预购</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180520213653lEDekCpKSV1buR7B.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.560386\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180520213653NYcZrvp4GgMjVIJq.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.564706\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180520213103YFKrGqeLf75u3Dwi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180520213103vcYoZQKAjwCHsiyd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180520213103Xqa0erUQb5YPhDiE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180520213104SWC8jZMknX9UwmcA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>The Kodiak Survival Paracord Bracelet by Outdoor Element</h3><p>科罗拉多户外品牌 Outdoor Element 推出了一款 Kodiak 户外生存手环，目标人群是那些经常去林区野营的人群。有人将其形容为“手腕上的瑞士军刀”。卡扣处是一对打火机，手环本身由 2.4 米长的耐磨绳索编织而成，里面还藏了一个钢制鱼钩，两条鱼线和一块助燃火绒，使用起来非常方便。售价 24.99 美元，<a href=\"https://www.outdoorelement.com/product/kodiak/\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=p0660g2aj97&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180520213742lFUBgLje4sdCR7K6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180520213742Da3gFvGfhoYjUnM1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180520213742gyqxbcFkYs3T1mGh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180520213742I2fsHOG1oTJgQbr4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018052021374353P9cAKsxJL8GY6W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180520213743dtm0hcZzC7Y3oqNb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}